content: Seventh game (12.04.2021). Another Spanish opening. Sixth tie. Nepomniachtchi (white) 3 - Carlsen (black) 4.
translations: ita:Settima partita (04.12.2021). Un'altra apertura spagnola. Sesto pareggio. Nepomniachtchi (bianco) 3 - Carlsen (nero) 4
